Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,610)}藻床小朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到藻床小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now back to "The Kelpbed Kids"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藻床小朋友这片子也太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The Kelpbed Kids" are hilarious
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High four
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么是黑白的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonder why it's in black and white
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种选择很有艺术气息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a "artistical" choice
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  藻床小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Kelpbed Kids
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.27,0:01:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Youse gonna spill the beans
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.27,0:01:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把糖果藏到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about where you hide all your candy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.77,0:01:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这俱乐部什么地方  不然就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in this here clubhouse or else
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不告诉你  阿贾克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not to you, Ajax
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.95,0:01:39.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不可能告诉你就藏在柜子里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:39.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll never tell you that it's in the cabinet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, gang
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这藻床小朋友是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, don't the Kelpbed Kids
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.87,0:01:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点像我们认识的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,kinda look like people we know?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,熟人个个我都不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know any people we know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说柜子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cabinet, you say
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.39,0:02:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoops?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,650)}糖果
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  阿贾克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ajax
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's empty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要让大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give everyone here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.98,0:02:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有家里老子  全都吃我一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and their old man a knuckle sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配奶酪吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With cheese?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配奶酪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想得逞  呆呆小呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no you don't, you dizzy ding dong
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被圈住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just got hooped
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.60,0:02:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈  圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoops, Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That settles it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们最爱的藻床小朋友就是圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoops is our favorite Kelpbed Kid
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿出我们的官方正品圈圈呼啦圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out our official Hoops hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我昨天在海贝网上买的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I bought on SeaBay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就想到了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Way ahead of ya, pally
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine shrunk
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大小可以调
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's adjustable
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈不一定非得是个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who says a hoop has to be round?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个宽松调整按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a relaxed-fit button
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我呼啦圈上面被谁写满了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone wrote all over my hula hoop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1032,420)}圈圈\N裤头村大街{\fnArial}17{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号\N{\fnArial}10776
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面印了个地址
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's an address printed on here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在裤头村里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得圈圈会不会就住在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's where Hoops lives?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could we?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should we?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按了他家门铃就跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ring his doorbell and run away?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿厕纸撒满他家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toilet-paper his house?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.94,0:03:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.57,0:03:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他的普通咖啡换成无咖啡因的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Switch out his regular for decaf?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.07,0:03:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是可以去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can meet him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.41,0:03:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以去见他  然后拿厕纸撒满他家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can meet him, then toilet-paper his house
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.25,0:03:54.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他喝完咖啡一定用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:54.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's gonna need it after the coffee
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where Hoops lives
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个豪宅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a palace
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太紧张  不敢敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm too nervous to knock
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且咱都没完全认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't really know him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一他是那种老是受苦的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if he's one of those suffering artist types
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还沉迷于巫术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who are into witchcraft?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一他是食人族  想吃我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or what if he's a cannibal and wants to eat us?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一他是食人族  不想吃我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if he's a cannibal and doesn't want to eat us?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能忍受这种耻辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We couldn't live with the shame
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,助步器老头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Walker?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在圈圈家干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's he doing in Hoops' house?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能我们找错房子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we got the wrong house
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没收到邮件  非常难过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's sad that he got no mail
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为全被我收走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收件者是圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's addressed to Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这里没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the right place
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,324)}藻床笨笨\N小朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房子里全是藻床小朋友的周边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The whole house is filled with "Kelpbed Kid" stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像在出演节目一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just like being in the show
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1152,188)}可疑鱼钩
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752,234)}为了圈圈好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是圈圈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that Hoops?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.55,0:05:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是助步器老头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Old Man Walker again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前开邮箱那位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From the mailbox?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooligans
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Swindlers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷信贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Letter looters
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们没想对你干坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean any harm
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是想见见圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to meet Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're fans
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoops?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然不想说得这么直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate to break it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但圈圈是个小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Hoops is a little kid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我小时候就是圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, I was Hoops when I was a little kid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经是多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,many years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在说有很多年了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're telling me there have been many years?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.14,0:06:16.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  都是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:16.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was in the past
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怕是想把我们骗过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're trying to "past" one over on us
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Past" one over
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们又算老几  呆呆小呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you, a couple of dizzy ding dongs?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说了圈圈的口头禅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said Hoops' catchphrase
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呆呆小呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Ya dizzy ding dongs"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呆呆小呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ya dizzy ding dongs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  助步器老头就是圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, "Old Man" Walker is Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.71,0:06:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是稍微有点  腐烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He just kinda, sorta, decayed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你快害我骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're breaking my bones
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他有新的口头禅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got a new catchphrase
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的心脏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that my heart?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是外面传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it was outside
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我心脏跑外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My heart's outside?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dagnabbit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个恶棍  阿贾克斯麦基
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's that ruffian, Ajax McGee
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.92,0:07:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿贾克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ajax?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不是藻床小朋友那位坏小孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't he the mean kid in "The Kelpbed Kids" show?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他长成坏大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now he's the mean adult
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就住在荫凉滩疗养院里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at Shady Shoals Retirement Home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.02,0:07:42.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当个藻床小朋友就是这么个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:42.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for being a Kelpbed Kid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoops the Poops
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈圈讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoops the Poops
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Classic
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just had an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Revenge
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.08,0:08:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反击阿贾克斯  复现你演过的剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get back at Ajax, like in one of your episodes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶疾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Episodes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.96,0:08:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这年纪确实发作了很多次恶疾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at my age, I have a lot of episodes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想吃布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants pudding?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别布丁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold that pudding
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以自制坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can build our own tank
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.76,0:08:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用藻床小朋友法集齐材料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we'll gather material "The Kelpbed Kids" way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么床谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The what bed who--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.81,0:08:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不愧是圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Classic Hoops
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414,380)}三轮车游行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来找你了  阿贾克斯麦基
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're coming for you, Ajax McGee
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,638)}凶巴巴撕碎机
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.86,0:09:20.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我的凶巴巴撕碎机问个好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:20.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to my Meanie Mangler
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,912)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了  圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are, Hoops
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,荫凉滩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shady Shoals
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来叫阿贾克斯出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now call out for Ajax
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼叫谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who am I calling?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对着这个讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talk into this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  接线生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, operator?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是梭鱼4117
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Barracuda 4117
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,处方备好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is my prescription ready yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我走开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,23 Skiddoo
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪找来的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that pile of junk?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正不关我事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind, I don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃点蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have some eggs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare cannon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.95,0:09:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:09:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是拿面包装弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You loaded the cannon with toast?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吃面包都会配蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always have toast with eggs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,部署舔盐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deploying salt lick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出动海牛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Engaging sea cow
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的舌头好粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your tongue is so rough
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有东西都有股面包味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything smells like toast
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  阿贾克斯落荒而逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, there goes Ajax
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次一定会整到你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get youse next time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say my name
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是讨厌鬼圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Hoops the Poops
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Classic
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史上最棒藻床小朋友大冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best "Kelpbed Kids" adventure ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High four
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我圈圈哎哟喂好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just call me Hoops the Oops
