Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty, up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.92,0:12:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪咪声都快逼疯我了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All this meeping is gonna drive me cuckoo, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们咪了  你才有工资拿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All these meeps are paying your salary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪就是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meeps are money
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty, up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.32,0:12:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  有人点了蟹黄堡打包外带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, someone ordered a Krabby Patty to-go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁点了蟹黄堡打包外带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who ordered a Krabby Patty to-go?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  这是谁点的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, whose order is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.60,0:13:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  有没有谁点了蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, did someone order a Krabby--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.94,0:13:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bad
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant meep, meep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1484,352)}高菲高伯
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  冰淇咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, ice meep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,520)}墨镜
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太咪了  酷哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real meep, daddy-o
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1226,294)}床垫
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.82,0:14:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弹弹跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bouncy, bouncy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love to meep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的手掌要来认真玩拍手烤蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These palms are ready to play some serious patty-cake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.89,0:14:36.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拍手烤蛋糕可不能缺了蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:36.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you can't play patty-cake without cake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拍拍手  烤蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patty-cake, patty-cake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.61,0:14:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烘焙师傅  我要快快吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Baker's man, I'll eat the cake as fast as I can
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈打电话找医生  医生说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama called the doctor, and the doctor said
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.53,0:14:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别又烤蛋糕又在床上跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"No more patty-cakes jumping on the bed"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该来上班了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about time, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟到宝宝还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,LateBob is more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟到宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,LateBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你哼哼完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you're done snorting
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来点个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个蟹黄堡  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, stop that meeping
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以为你什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think you are?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An anchovy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听到咪咪而来的钱声了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hear money meeps
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are the anchovies back?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the barnacles is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.68,0:16:39.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开  让我珍贵的菲菲过路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:39.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step aside and let my precious Fifi pass
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就要冒犯到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I will be offended
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一堆人咪过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a stamp-meep
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,858)}突发新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是鲍勃盖尔多普勒  播报天气情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob Gale Doppler, with the big weather
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天裤头村将会晴空万里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to report it's sunny skies for Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.72,0:17:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但今天正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not today
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.68,0:17:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即将发布一场暴风雨预警
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cause there's a storm warning coming at ya
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.10,0:17:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,西南方向正吹来一阵凤伪鱼狂风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got a gust of faux-chovies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming in from the southwest
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来实地探访一下  有请现场记者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now with a closer look, here's our man on the street
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金鱼鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rube Goldfish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Gale
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身边的正是这群凤伪鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here with the faux-chovies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们造成了这场咪咪混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that are causing all this meep-abaloo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.70,0:17:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来问问大家十分关切的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I just have to ask the question
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everyone wants to know
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪  到底是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the world does "meep" mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ameeping
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks Rube
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以如果今天不想变成凤尾鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if you don't wanna turn into an anchovy today
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议待在室内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're advised to stay indoors
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到凤伪鱼气压系统过境之后才出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until that faux-chovy pressure system moves away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,876)}开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:15.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,876)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是章鱼哥专属的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now it's Squiddy time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,712)}蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人全跑光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When the customers fizzle
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼晒日光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the octopus will sizzle
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.67,0:18:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的  吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dinner, dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的  吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dinner, dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.77,0:18:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝跟蟹老板变成凤伪鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Mr. Krabs are faux-chovies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,咪了很多声之后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡  一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty, one Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要蟹黄堡的都举手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever wants a Krabby Patty, raise your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带着耳机听不见你们咪咪叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear your meeping with these headphones on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.93,0:19:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别弄坏我的耳机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my headphones
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪咪声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The meeps
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难听的咪咪声全让我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can hear the horrible meeps
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又咪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More meeps?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼打群架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchovy rumble
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant meep, meep
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought that was you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.50,0:20:37.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界都疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:37.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The whole world has gone insane
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准再咪下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is the last meep
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1156,576)}匹萨店  特大匹萨
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地面匹萨世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surface World of Pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份特特特大号匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like an extra, extra, extra large pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽快送来蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sent to the Krusty Krab as soon as possible
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要匹萨尽快送到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want-a a pizza as soon-a as possible
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  小章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got it, Calimaro
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都没法把我变成凤伪鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody's turning me into a faux-chovy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,匹萨外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pizza delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,290)}匹萨
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pizza?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That smells good
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.86,0:21:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为会变凤伪鱼一辈子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd never snap out of that faux-chovy thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.54,0:21:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点没反应过来咪上头有多容易
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize how easy it is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get swept up into a meep mentality
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不怪你  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.25,0:22:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好匹萨是凤尾鱼的天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that pizza is the anchovies' natural enemy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.59,0:22:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  订派的那位救了我们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whoever ordered that pie saved our lives
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.14,0:22:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这好东西可不能浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we shouldn't let it go to waste
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还热乎着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still hot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没加凤尾鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No anchovies?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.44,0:22:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之前老是咪  害我也都饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All that meeping made me hungry too
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.36,0:22:29.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  给咱来几张纸盘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:29.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, we need some paper plates out here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.03,0:22:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个懒鬼跑哪混了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now just where is that lazy bum
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚明明一堆事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while all this is going on?
